From: Andrii Nakryiko <andriin@fb.com>
Date: Tue, 18 Aug 2020 15:39:14 -0700
Subject: libbpf: Clean up and improve CO-RE reloc logging
Patch-mainline: v5.10-rc1
Git-commit: 28b93c64499ae09d9dc8c04123b15f8654a93c4c
